<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA75">
<l>kalaṅku puṉalkaṅkai yūṭāla lālu</l>
<l>milaṅku matiyiyaṅka lālu - nalaṅkoḷ</l>
<l>paricuṭaiyā ṉīṇmuṭimēṟ pāmpiyaṅka lālum</l>
<l>viricaṭaiyāṅ kāṇil vicumpu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>By the movement of the Gaṅgā with agitated waves,</l>
<l>by the stirring of the shining moon, by the stirring of the snake</l>
<l>on the long crown of him with good qualities,</l>
<l>the broad matted hair is, when one looks, the sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
